title: cuisine-french-onion-soup
caption: French Onion Soup
tags: cuisine
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Slowly caramelised onions in beef stock, topped with a crouton and a thick layer of Gruyère, then grilled until the cheese bubbles.  The long caramelisation (45–60 minutes over low heat) is what gives the soup its deep colour and sweetness.
